title: Executive Order 6193-Revocation of Withdrawal of Public Lands Pending Resurvey, New Mexico
content: It is hereby ordered that Executive Order No. 5555, dated February 11, 1931, which withdrew the public lands in T. 15 N., R. 18 W. of the New Mexico principal meridian, New Mexico, pending a resurvey, be, and the same is hereby, revoked.
citation: Franklin D. Roosevelt, Executive Order 6193-Revocation of Withdrawal of Public Lands Pending Resurvey, New Mexico Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/362012
